@startuml
scale 1
skinparam defaultFontSize 14
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ParticipantPadding 80
skinparam BoxPadding 40

actor "User" as U
participant "Web\nApplication" as W
participant "Backend\nAPI" as B
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

== Page Load ==

U -> W: Navigate to /issues
W -> W: Read active team\nfrom Zustand

W -> B: GET /issue-types
B -> DB: Query issue types
DB -> B: IssueType list
B -> W: IssueTypeBaseResponse[]

W -> B: GET /issues\n?teamId=X&view=issues\n&page=1&pageSize=10
B -> B: @PreAuthorize\nteam membership check
B -> DB: Query issue IDs\n(filtered, paginated)
DB -> B: Matching IDs
B -> DB: Fetch full issues by IDs\n(with joins: type, creator, team)
DB -> B: Issue entities
B -> W: PagedEntityResponse
W -> U: Display issues table

== View Filtering ==

U -> W: Switch to "Long Term" tab
W -> B: GET /issues\n?teamId=X&view=long_term
B -> DB: Query where type\n= "Long Term Issue"
DB -> B: Filtered issues
B -> W: Paginated list
W -> U: Display long-term issues

== Create Issue ==

U -> W: Fill issue dialog + submit
W -> B: POST /issues\n{teamId, title,\ndescription, issueTypeId}
B -> B: Validate team membership
B -> B: Validate issue type
B -> DB: INSERT issue
DB -> B: Saved issue
B -> W: IssueResponse
W -> W: Invalidate query cache
W -> U: Updated issues list

== Update Issue ==

U -> W: Edit issue + submit
W -> B: PUT /issues/{id}\n{title, description, issueTypeId}
B -> B: Validate team membership
B -> DB: UPDATE issue
DB -> B: Updated issue
B -> W: IssueResponse
W -> U: Show updated issue

== Archive / Delete ==

alt Archive
    U -> W: Click archive
    W -> B: PATCH /issues/{id}\n{isArchived: true}
    B -> DB: UPDATE isArchived
    B -> W: IssueResponse
else Delete
    U -> W: Click delete + confirm
    W -> B: DELETE /issues/{id}
    B -> DB: DELETE issue
    B -> W: 204 No Content
end

W -> W: Invalidate query cache
W -> U: Updated view

@enduml
